text: Reminder: from 1-2pm today I'll be doing some slides and demos about iOS/OS X's Auto Layout system in the Social Space. All are welcome! The first part will be basics and UI/Storyboarding process. The second part will be Code. A very short Animation bit at the end.

Hey everyone - we have Carmen Merlo joining us at 11am today for a discussion about Portland’s preparation for the earthquake. (In addition to being a mandatory meeting - this should be an amazing opportunity to learn about what the state is doing, what you can do to prepare yourself and your families, and  begin to think about how we might put Uncorked’s resources toward helping inform our neighbors and friends. Looking forward to seeing you there.)
